<i>adjective</i>: 입바르다 [입빠르다], 곧다 [곧따] <i>determiner</i>: 직선적 [직썬적], 단적 [단쩍], 단도직입적 [단도지깁쩍] <i>noun</i>: 단적 [단쩍], 단도직입적 [단도지깁쩍] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>입바르다 [입빠르다]</dt><br>
<dd>unreserved; straightforward; outspoken</dd><br>
<dd>바른말을 하는 데 막힘이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>Not hesitating in speaking right words.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>곧다 [곧따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. straight; upright; direct</dd><br>
<dd>길, 선, 자세 등이 휘지 않고 똑바르다.</dd><br>
<dd>A road, line, posture, etc., being straight, not bent.</dd><br>
<dd>2. honest; straightforward</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 정직하고 바르다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being honest and upright.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>determiner</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>직선적 [직썬적]</dt><br>
<dd>1. straight</dd><br>
<dd>꺾이거나 굽은 데가 없이 곧게 뻗은.</dd><br>
<dd>Being straight, neither curved nor bent.</dd><br>
<dd>2. straightforward</dd><br>
<dd>꾸미거나 숨기지 않고 있는 그대로의 솔직한.</dd><br>
<dd>Being straightforward without concealment or fabrication.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단적 [단쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>straightforward; point-blank</dd><br>
<dd>분명하고 직접적인.</dd><br>
<dd>Clear and direct.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단도직입적 [단도지깁쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>direct; straightforward; point blank; blunt</dd><br>
<dd>쓸데없는 말은 빼고 곧바로 중요한 말을 하는.</dd><br>
<dd>Cutting to the chase or getting right to the point without preamble.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단적 [단쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>direct; straightforward</dd><br>
<dd>분명하고 직접적인 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Being clear and direct.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단도직입적 [단도지깁쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>point-blank; straightforward; speaking without preamble</dd><br>
<dd>쓸데없는 말은 빼고 곧바로 중요한 말을 하는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of saying something important in a straightforward way, without beating about the bush.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>